    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>从线性化的Wigner-Moyal方程和泊松方程出发，推导色散关系的步骤如下：</p><hr><h3 id="推导过程"><a href="#推导过程" class="headerlink" title="推导过程"></a>推导过程</h3><h4 id="1-线性化假设"><a href="#1-线性化假设" class="headerlink" title="1. 线性化假设"></a>1. <strong>线性化假设</strong></h4><p>假设Wigner函数和电势具有小振幅平面波扰动：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W(\mathbf{r},\mathbf{p},t) = W_0(\mathbf{p}) + W_1(\mathbf{p}) e^{i k z - i \omega t},</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\phi(\mathbf{r},t) = \phi_1 e^{i k z - i \omega t},</script><p>其中 $W_0(\mathbf{p})$ 是均匀背景分布，$W_1(\mathbf{p})$ 和 $\phi_1$ 是扰动项。</p><hr><h4 id="2-代入Wigner-Moyal方程"><a href="#2-代入Wigner-Moyal方程" class="headerlink" title="2. 代入Wigner-Moyal方程"></a>2. <strong>代入Wigner-Moyal方程</strong></h4><p>静电情形下，Wigner-Moyal方程为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\partial_t W + \frac{\mathbf{p}}{m} \cdot \nabla_r W = \frac{q}{\hbar} \left[ \phi\left(\mathbf{r} + \frac{i\hbar}{2} \nabla_p, t\right) - \phi\left(\mathbf{r} - \frac{i\hbar}{2} \nabla_p, t\right) \right] W.</script><p>线性化后保留一阶扰动项，扰动方程化简为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">-i \omega W_1 + i k \frac{p_z}{m} W_1 = \frac{q}{\hbar} \phi_1 \left[ W_0\left(\mathbf{p} + \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) - W_0\left(\mathbf{p} - \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) \right].</script><p>解得：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W_1(\mathbf{p}) = \frac{q \phi_1}{\hbar (\omega - k p_z/m)} \left[ W_0\left(\mathbf{p} + \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) - W_0\left(\mathbf{p} - \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) \right].</script><hr><h4 id="3-代入泊松方程"><a href="#3-代入泊松方程" class="headerlink" title="3. 代入泊松方程"></a>3. <strong>代入泊松方程</strong></h4><p>电荷密度为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">n_1 = \int d^3 p \, W_1(\mathbf{p}) = \frac{q \phi_1}{\hbar} \int d^3 p \, \frac{W_0\left(\mathbf{p} + \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) - W_0\left(\mathbf{p} - \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right)}{\omega - k p_z/m}.</script><p>泊松方程为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">k^2 \phi_1 = \frac{q n_1}{\epsilon_0}.</script><p>联立得色散关系：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">1 + \frac{q^2}{\epsilon_0 \hbar k^2} \int d^3 p \, \frac{W_0\left(\mathbf{p} + \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) - W_0\left(\mathbf{p} - \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right)}{\omega - k p_z/m} = 0. \quad \text{(1)}</script><hr><h4 id="4-变量替换简化积分"><a href="#4-变量替换简化积分" class="headerlink" title="4. 变量替换简化积分"></a>4. <strong>变量替换简化积分</strong></h4><p>令 <script type="math/tex">\mathbf{p}' = \mathbf{p} \pm \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}</script>，则分子差分为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W_0\left(\mathbf{p} + \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) - W_0\left(\mathbf{p} - \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}\right) = W_0(\mathbf{p}') \bigg|_{\mathbf{p}' = \mathbf{p} + \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}} - W_0(\mathbf{p}') \bigg|_{\mathbf{p}' = \mathbf{p} - \frac{\hbar k \mathbf{\hat{z}}}{2}}.</script><p>将积分变量换回 $\mathbf{p}’$，并利用对称性，原色散关系(1)可改写为：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">1 - \frac{q^2}{m \epsilon_0} \int d^3 p \, \frac{W_0(\mathbf{p})}{\left( \omega - k p_z/m \right)^2 - \hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2} = 0. \quad \text{(2)}</script><p><strong>关键步骤</strong>：<br>• 差商形式对应动量导数的离散化，即 <script type="math/tex">\Delta W_0 \approx \hbar k \partial_{p_z} W_0</script><br>• 分母 $\omega - k p_z/m$ 在积分中通过变量替换和泰勒展开转换为平方项，引入量子修正 <script type="math/tex">\hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2</script></p><hr><h3 id="最终色散关系"><a href="#最终色散关系" class="headerlink" title="最终色散关系"></a>最终色散关系</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">1 - \frac{q^2}{m \epsilon_0} \int d^3 p \, \frac{W_0(\mathbf{p})}{\left( \omega - k p_z/m \right)^2 - \hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2} = 0.</script><hr><h3 id="物理意义"><a href="#物理意义" class="headerlink" title="物理意义"></a>物理意义</h3><p>• <strong>经典极限 ($\hbar \to 0$)</strong>：退化为Vlasov色散关系 $1 - \frac{q^2}{m \epsilon_0} \int \frac{W_0(\mathbf{p})}{(\omega - k p_z/m)^2} d^3 p = 0$.<br>• <strong>量子修正</strong>：$\hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2$ 项反映波矢引起的动量空间离散效应，抑制共振（如Landau阻尼）。</p><span id="more"></span>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;从线性化的Wigner-Moyal方程和泊松方程出发，推导色散关系的步骤如下：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;推导过程&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#推导过程&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;推导过程&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;推导过程&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;1-线性化假设&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-线性化假设&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1. 线性化假设&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. &lt;strong&gt;线性化假设&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;假设Wigner函数和电势具有小振幅平面波扰动：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
W(&#92;mathbf{r},&#92;mathbf{p},t) = W_0(&#92;mathbf{p}) + W_1(&#92;mathbf{p}) e^{i k z - i &#92;omega t},&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
&#92;phi(&#92;mathbf{r},t) = &#92;phi_1 e^{i k z - i &#92;omega t},&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;其中 $W_0(&#92;mathbf{p})$ 是均匀背景分布，$W_1(&#92;mathbf{p})$ 和 $&#92;phi_1$ 是扰动项。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;2-代入Wigner-Moyal方程&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#2-代入Wigner-Moyal方程&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;2. 代入Wigner-Moyal方程&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;2. &lt;strong&gt;代入Wigner-Moyal方程&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;静电情形下，Wigner-Moyal方程为：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
&#92;partial_t W + &#92;frac{&#92;mathbf{p}}{m} &#92;cdot &#92;nabla_r W = &#92;frac{q}{&#92;hbar} &#92;left[ &#92;phi&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{r} + &#92;frac{i&#92;hbar}{2} &#92;nabla_p, t&#92;right) - &#92;phi&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{r} - &#92;frac{i&#92;hbar}{2} &#92;nabla_p, t&#92;right) &#92;right] W.&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;线性化后保留一阶扰动项，扰动方程化简为：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
-i &#92;omega W_1 + i k &#92;frac{p_z}{m} W_1 = &#92;frac{q}{&#92;hbar} &#92;phi_1 &#92;left[ W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} + &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) - W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} - &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) &#92;right].&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;解得：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
W_1(&#92;mathbf{p}) = &#92;frac{q &#92;phi_1}{&#92;hbar (&#92;omega - k p_z/m)} &#92;left[ W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} + &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) - W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} - &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) &#92;right].&lt;/script&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;3-代入泊松方程&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#3-代入泊松方程&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;3. 代入泊松方程&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;3. &lt;strong&gt;代入泊松方程&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;电荷密度为：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
n_1 = &#92;int d^3 p &#92;, W_1(&#92;mathbf{p}) = &#92;frac{q &#92;phi_1}{&#92;hbar} &#92;int d^3 p &#92;, &#92;frac{W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} + &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) - W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} - &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right)}{&#92;omega - k p_z/m}.&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;泊松方程为：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
k^2 &#92;phi_1 = &#92;frac{q n_1}{&#92;epsilon_0}.&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;联立得色散关系：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
1 + &#92;frac{q^2}{&#92;epsilon_0 &#92;hbar k^2} &#92;int d^3 p &#92;, &#92;frac{W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} + &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) - W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} - &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right)}{&#92;omega - k p_z/m} = 0. &#92;quad &#92;text{(1)}&lt;/script&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;4-变量替换简化积分&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#4-变量替换简化积分&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;4. 变量替换简化积分&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;4. &lt;strong&gt;变量替换简化积分&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;令 &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;&#92;mathbf{p}&#39; = &#92;mathbf{p} &#92;pm &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&lt;/script&gt;，则分子差分为：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} + &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) - W_0&#92;left(&#92;mathbf{p} - &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}&#92;right) = W_0(&#92;mathbf{p}&#39;) &#92;bigg|_{&#92;mathbf{p}&#39; = &#92;mathbf{p} + &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}} - W_0(&#92;mathbf{p}&#39;) &#92;bigg|_{&#92;mathbf{p}&#39; = &#92;mathbf{p} - &#92;frac{&#92;hbar k &#92;mathbf{&#92;hat{z}}}{2}}.&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;将积分变量换回 $&#92;mathbf{p}’$，并利用对称性，原色散关系(1)可改写为：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
1 - &#92;frac{q^2}{m &#92;epsilon_0} &#92;int d^3 p &#92;, &#92;frac{W_0(&#92;mathbf{p})}{&#92;left( &#92;omega - k p_z/m &#92;right)^2 - &#92;hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2} = 0. &#92;quad &#92;text{(2)}&lt;/script&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键步骤&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;br&gt;• 差商形式对应动量导数的离散化，即 &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;&#92;Delta W_0 &#92;approx &#92;hbar k &#92;partial_{p_z} W_0&lt;/script&gt;&lt;br&gt;• 分母 $&#92;omega - k p_z/m$ 在积分中通过变量替换和泰勒展开转换为平方项，引入量子修正 &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;&#92;hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;最终色散关系&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#最终色散关系&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;最终色散关系&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;最终色散关系&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;
1 - &#92;frac{q^2}{m &#92;epsilon_0} &#92;int d^3 p &#92;, &#92;frac{W_0(&#92;mathbf{p})}{&#92;left( &#92;omega - k p_z/m &#92;right)^2 - &#92;hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2} = 0.&lt;/script&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;物理意义&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#物理意义&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;物理意义&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;物理意义&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;• &lt;strong&gt;经典极限 ($&#92;hbar &#92;to 0$)&lt;/strong&gt;：退化为Vlasov色散关系 $1 - &#92;frac{q^2}{m &#92;epsilon_0} &#92;int &#92;frac{W_0(&#92;mathbf{p})}{(&#92;omega - k p_z/m)^2} d^3 p = 0$.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;strong&gt;量子修正&lt;/strong&gt;：$&#92;hbar^2 k^4 / 4 m^2$ 项反映波矢引起的动量空间离散效应，抑制共振（如Landau阻尼）。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
